    "long_instructions": "## Do This:\r\n1. Create a `Painter` object.\r\n2. Add methods to move the `Painter` to the cone.\r\n\t- **Hint:** Use your pseudocode on the activity guide for Task 2: A to C.\r\n    \r\n---\r\n###AI Tutor Support\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure how to create and move a Painter?**]\r\nAsk AI: \r\n- How do I create a `Painter` object in Python?\r\n- Which method makes the Painter move forward?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [**Stuck on getting to the cone?**]\r\nAsk AI:\r\n- How do I move the Painter multiple steps?\r\n- How do I get the Painter to turn around?\r\n:::\r\n",
    "start_sources": {
      "files": {
        "0": {
          "id": "0",
          "name": "main.py",
          "language": "py",
          "contents": "from neighborhood import Painter\n#add the painter object below\n\n#add methods below to move the painter\n",
          "folderId": "0",
          "active": false,
          "open": true,
          "type": "locked_starter"
